data.description: Cute Cape Cod in desirable neighborhood in Willowick.  Original hardwood floors, some new paint, arched doorways and beautiful solid wood entry door.  This home has a bedroom on the main level with a full bathroom nearby with newer tile floor.  There is a large eat-in kitchen and a nice size living room.  There are two additional bedrooms on the second floor including a half bath.  The property has a large yard and detached 2 car garage.  Call today for a private showing.
